description:
Use your mouse to fly around this little astronaut guy.
I edited a squid CodePen online to make this.
So basically, this guy is a coloured squid, with only two tentacles, squirting alot of white 'ink'. To create the aesthetic that he's an astronaut.

Original Squid CodePen:
https://codepen.io/pimskie/pen/XgaevB
title: Little Interactive Astronaut
